cells: MEDIUM = setup to a core comm
GREEN = start with thumb on F face
BLUE = regrip to thumb on D face
RED = regrip to thumb on U face
Core commutators are either pure <RUD> (8 moves) or the same but with one move setup on the interchange layer (9 moves).
PURPLE = regrip to thumb on B face (avoid if possible!)
LAVENDER = regrip with left hand instead
